.BR mi_open_obj (),
.BR mi_close_obj ()
and
.BR mi_close_size ()
are
.I OpenSS7 Project
functions based loosely on the
.BR mi_open_alloc (9)
and
.BR mi_close_free (9)
Mentat functions.
